{"tid":2417683,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"FT：滙豐退出美國消費銀行業務 高層指杜嘉祺80%精力處理政治問題","createTime":"2021-02-22T05:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T05:56:59.000Z","uid":239336,"like":204,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"d14868aa8dde7542454c38c3eb2e39d884a5ac9a","tid":2417683,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"滙豐控股（005）將於周二（23日）公佈業績，英國《金融時報》引述消息人士指，該行屆時會宣佈退出美國消費銀行業務，認為深陷困境的部門難以逆轉，並制定「重返亞洲（Pivot to Asia）」策略，數名高層將由倫敦調回香港。滙豐對報道不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐美國零售銀行業務涉及150間分行，退出標誌着該行40年來在美經營的終結。據報，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">滙豐一位知名高層透露，滙豐計劃擴張中國和其他快速增長的市場，包括新加坡和印度，並正為將來在新加坡進行一筆收購奠定基礎，但業績日暫不公佈詳情</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n有傳遷往香港的高層，包括環球銀行及資本市場聯席主管Greg Guyett、財富管理及個人銀行業務全球行政總裁Nuno Matos及全球商業銀行業務行政總裁Barry O&rsquo;Byrne，一旦調遷屬實，意味着2019年為滙豐進賬多達95%收入的部門，將集中在香港。<br />\n<br />\n近年匯豐一直捲入政治紛爭中，包括在2016年底被批「出賣華為」，配合美國司法部調查華為，使高管孟晚舟被捕；又被中方批評在《港區國安法》立法上，遲遲未表態。該行隨後表示支持立法並凍結民主派人士戶口，特首林鄭月娥亦公開稱，非常樂見滙豐在香港做大做強。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一名滙豐高層直言，滙豐主席杜嘉祺（Mark Tucker）目前80%處理政治問題，只得20%用以處理公司業務，形容「中國人有潛力摧毀他們。（The Chinese have the potential to destroy them.）」<br />\n<br />\n早於去年2月，滙豐在美國和歐洲裁員3.5萬人，釋放1,000億美元風險加權資產，轉投增長更快的亞洲和中東地區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210222/QCAMPRHGEJA6FJJ4BOOL7PSL7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210222%2FQCAMPRHGEJA6FJJ4BOOL7PSL7M%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=c15a310d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210222%2FQCAMPRHGEJA6FJJ4BOOL7PSL7M%2F&h=20bdcf8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210222/QCAMPRHGEJA6FJJ4BOOL7PSL7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Lqms9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Lqms9i.png&h=ac4410df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c75e71a7e2cd479e770eb1124884db83d03d048a","tid":2417683,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fd5115caa5682e4438861a4368d9c3ad12bbd4","tid":2417683,"uid":51469,"like":9,"dislike":20,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"CCTOY不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b2dbe6fa2d8d8d861be057f8ee71de209a8d0a","tid":2417683,"uid":191926,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"匯豐戶口得番1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其餘的錢轉哂去firstrade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc69211144c474cbc64b41b0d789c618b75fb7b1","tid":2417683,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b9b2dbe6fa2d8d8d861be057f8ee71de209a8d0a","tid":2417683,"uid":191926,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"匯豐戶口得番1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其餘的錢轉哂去firstrade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"我得返1毫子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3d4da6add9ada84e600b3b481c3e95c2bcb6a4","tid":2417683,"uid":326140,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:45:38.000Z","msg":"遲啲印度同中國咪又打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdb8e914c85eb1fe41790507deeae3b445b9917","tid":2417683,"uid":13503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"退出埋美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1319ad4d374866610ee1b1f7e71f0c4a12ff2f6a","tid":2417683,"uid":37874,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:47:37.000Z","msg":